about.summary: OpenStack Object Storage API Client Library

name: python-swiftclient
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "python-swiftclient" %}
{% set version = "3.8.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 3a013303643f77a99befa05582dfb93671e1fba1aed9f4a517418129700aedb8

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  entry_points:
    - swift = swiftclient.shell:main

requirements:
  host:
    - pbr
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - futures >=3.0.0  # [py==27]
    - python
    - requests
    - setuptools
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - swiftclient

about:
  home: https://docs.openstack.org/python-swiftclient/latest/
  license: Apache Software
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "OpenStack Object Storage API Client Library"
  doc_url: https://docs.openstack.org/python-swiftclient/latest/
  dev_url: https://opendev.org/openstack/python-swiftclient

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
